title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>For all finite sets <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>, we have:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \mathord {\#}{\mathrm {Bij}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}} =  \begin {cases}   0 &\text {if } \mathord {\#}{A}\not =\mathord {\#}{B}\\   n!&\text {if } \mathord {\#}{A}=\mathord {\#}{B}=n  \end {cases} ]]></fr:tex>
 
   
   <fr:tree
toc="false"
